## ğŸŒ† Overview

This project generates a **photorealistic 3D render** of **Nairobi, Kenya**, using **OpenStreetMap (OSM)** spatial data and the **rayrender** package in R.  
The script automatically retrieves map features within a 1 km radius around Nairobiâ€™s city center and renders them as 3D objects with realistic lighting and materials.

